#include<iostream>
#include<algorithm>
#include<vector>
#include<cmath>
#include<cstring>
#include<string>
using namespace std;
int z[2000];
int main()
{
  string num;
  vector<int>v;
  int i,j;
  for(i=2;i*i<2000;i++)
   for(j=2*i;j<2000;j+=i)
    z[j]=1;
   for(i=2;i<2000;i++)//must be carefull if we put i=0 to means it is divide by zero error
    if(!z[i])
     v.push_back(i);
   cin>>num;
   if(num=="0"||num=="1")
   {
    printf("COMPOSITE\n");
    return 0;
    }
   else
   {
     for(i=0;i<v.size();i++)
     {
      int t=0;
      for(j=0;j<num.size()&&t<=v[i];j++)
      {
       t=10*t+num[j]-'0';
       }
      if(t==v[i])
      {
       printf("PRIME\n");
       return 0;
       }
       t=t%v[i];
       for(;j<num.size();j++)
       {
         t=10*t+num[j]-'0';
         t=t%v[i];
         }
       if(t==0)
       {
        printf("COMPOSITE\n");
        return 0;
        }
       }
       printf("PRIME\n");
     }
    return 0;
}
